# Squad Search

## Dominio

Busca global full-text via Elasticsearch: indexacao near real-time, busca unificada, reindexacao via fila, fallback PostgreSQL. Alimenta o Command Menu (Cmd+K) do frontend.

**Fonte de verdade:** PLANO.md secao 2.13 (Search completo — indices, arquitetura, padroes)
**Fase PLANO:** F4B (construcao) + ownership continuo

---

## Entidades/Recursos sob responsabilidade

| Recurso | Secao PLANO |
|---|---|
| SearchModule | 2.13 |
| SearchService (busca + fallback PG) | 2.13 |
| SearchRepository (client @elastic/elasticsearch) | 2.13 |
| SearchIndexerService (listener EventEmitter2) | 2.13 |
| SearchReindexProcessor (BullMQ worker) | 2.13 |
| 5 indices ES: mundial_clients, mundial_products, mundial_orders, mundial_invoices, mundial_suppliers | 2.13 |
| Endpoints: GET /search, POST /search/reindex, GET /search/health | 2.13 |

